  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bare Knuckle Sandwich is a 2D boxing game featuring side-scrolling storytelling and a character driven narrative. Follow Gunner as he joins an underground bare-knuckle boxing ring looking for something to strive for in a world full of con-artists, grifters, and people just trying to get by. After meeting a new mentor, Gunner begins to find his footing after a rough start to adulthood. However, it's a long way to the top and he'll have to overcome everyone standing in his way to succeed, especially himself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras/3fc98c28e0702c000bff0b163c9988cb.avif?t=1766083764\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras_big/3fc98c28e0702c000bff0b163c9988cb.avif?t=1766083764 width=800 height=260 /></span>Enter the ring and fight unique opponents, each with their own fight style and tricks up their sleeves. Fight your way up the ladder of victory and make a name for yourself amongst the best fighters the city has to offer. Master quick reactions, precise dodging, and devastating strikes to send your opponents reeling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras/606d6ee7a5a1e3bee5b04040b8accd60.poster.avif?t=1766083764\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras/606d6ee7a5a1e3bee5b04040b8accd60.webm?t=1766083764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras/606d6ee7a5a1e3bee5b04040b8accd60.mp4?t=1766083764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras/47a8edd0b534c598ae48d1c75e8ad496.avif?t=1766083764\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras_big/47a8edd0b534c598ae48d1c75e8ad496.avif?t=1766083764 width=800 height=260 /></span>Experience Gunner’s personal journey of early adulthood through hand-crafted dialogue and cutscenes. Between fights, explore the city and mingle with the locals. Meet a variety of interesting people and help Gunner make a friend or two. His rise to the top will also attract brutal enemies.  <br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras/20da22fe3898778de4c2bc46bf7ec49a.poster.avif?t=1766083764\" width=800 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras/20da22fe3898778de4c2bc46bf7ec49a.webm?t=1766083764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras/20da22fe3898778de4c2bc46bf7ec49a.mp4?t=1766083764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras/808f8748b9a5ad70c59244ce3a95979f.avif?t=1766083764\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras_big/808f8748b9a5ad70c59244ce3a95979f.avif?t=1766083764 width=800 height=260 /></span>Training to be the best bare-knuckle boxer around takes a lot of time, but it doesn't pay the bills. Perform a variety of side hustles to earn some extra cash.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras/c30148d021f8e290c67f551806b243c6.avif?t=1766083764\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras_big/c30148d021f8e290c67f551806b243c6.avif?t=1766083764 width=800 height=260 /></span>Bare Knuckle Sandwich features music by the artist Torture World setting the atmosphere during exploration, fights, and cutscenes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras/812e383a3bb8d32c1ef935d505be456d.poster.avif?t=1766083764\" width=800 height=498 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras/812e383a3bb8d32c1ef935d505be456d.webm?t=1766083764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2486370/extras/812e383a3bb8d32c1ef935d505be456d.mp4?t=1766083764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
